calcpad-gui — Linux GTK 4 frontend for CalcpadCE
================================================

This application is an independent graphical user interface that invokes
the CalcpadCE command-line tool (Calcpad.Cli) as an external subprocess.
No source code from CalcpadCE is bundled or directly linked.

